{"tid":1171534,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"震驚！Macbook pro 推出 八核 i9 版本","createTime":"2019-05-25T18:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T05:48:07.000Z","uid":127532,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dc83534e7837b971b7cd66f03a9d90f94b0a6431","tid":1171534,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:40:42.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，2018 macbook 突破科技界限，首次研發出第一部 i9 慢過i7既notebook<br />\n不過呢個技術好快就俾人破解，當中既橋妙就係將部機整薄佢，令佢儲藏熱空氣，令cpu溫度急速提升，從而降低效能<br />\n呢個做法既好處係唔須要為左散熱影響外型設計，令佢可以繼續潮爆銀色系<br />\n至今好多消費者都唔明，既然 i9 慢過 i7，咁點解要俾多D錢買 i9 呢？提出呢個問題既人忽略左mac機用家既一大特徵︰感覺。見到個 specs寫住 i9，佢地自然就會感覺良好，呢點只有蘋果呢間設有催眠部既公司做到<br />\n<br />\n言歸正傳，2019年，蘋果重施故技，推出macbook pro八核心版本，重點係外型設計無變<br />\n究竟今次呢部機有無保留到 i9 慢過 i7 既技術？<br />\n我地一於拭目以待"},{"pid":"f3a816c05b7000115c3dcce1a79e480ddc2db9d9","tid":1171534,"uid":127532,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:41:48.000Z","msg":"Macbook pro 2018 i9慢過 i7 的蘋果黑科技<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Apple-MacBook-Pro-15-Core-i9-slower-than-Core-i7.396971.0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.notebookcheck.net%2FApple-MacBook-Pro-15-Core-i9-slower-than-Core-i7.396971.0.html&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=374977be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.notebookcheck.net/Apple-MacBook-Pro-15-Core-i9-slower-than-Core-i7.396971.0.html</a><br />\n//Once you start to stress more cores, however, the Core i9-8950HK is slower than the Core i7-8850H, even during the first Cinebench run. The average result during our CB R15 Multi loop is 1007 points, while the Core i7 manages 1031 points on average. This means you pay a high premium for effectively less performance.//"},{"pid":"c6c2e63780075a450aafc809aca6d3bd77e3594f","tid":1171534,"uid":127532,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:42:48.000Z","msg":"外國 KOL 力推 macbook pro 2019<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jPFiDIYUUxo\" data-